"Optional parameters you’d like to pass with your placement. These can be referenced within the rules","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of your campaign. Keys beginning with ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"$"},{"text":" are reserved for Superwall and will be dropped. Values can be any","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"JSON encodable value, URLs or Dates. Arrays and dictionaries as values are not supported at this time, and will","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"be dropped.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"params"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An optional ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallOverrides","type":"reference"},{"text":" object whose parameters override the paywall defaults. Use this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to override products and whether it ignores the subscription status. Defaults to ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"paywallOverrides"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An optional completion block that gets called when the paywall should dismiss. This defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" and the SDK"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"presentationMode.wrappedValue.dismiss()"},{"type":"text","text":" by default. Otherwise you must perform the dismissal of the paywall."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"onRequestDismiss"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A completion block that accepts a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallSkippedReason"},{"type":"text","text":" and returns an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":". This will show"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when the requested paywall is skipped. Defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"EmptyView()"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"name":"onSkippedView"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A completion block containing a feature that you wish to paywall. Access to this block is remotely configurable via the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/superwall.com\/dashboard","type":"reference"},{"text":". If the paywall is set to ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Non Gated","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":", this will be called when","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the paywall is dismissed or if the user is already paying. If the paywall is ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Gated"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":", this will be called only if the user is already paying","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or if they begin paying. If no paywall is configured, this gets called immediately. This will not be called in the event of an error.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"feature"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This uses ","type":"text"},{"code":"Superwall\/getPaywall(forPlacement:params:paywallOverrides:delegate:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" under the hood."}]},{"style":"warning","name":"Warning","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You’re responsible for the deallocation of this view. If you have a ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" presented somewhere","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and you try to present the same ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" elsewhere, you will get a crash.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/docu